original_title: UFC Fight Night 147: Till vs. Masvidal
overview: UFC Fight Night 147: Till vs. Masvidal was a mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship held on March 16, 2019 at The O2 Arena in London, England. A welterweight bout between former UFC Welterweight Championship challenger Darren Till and Jorge Masvidal served as the event headliner.
title: UFC Fight Night 147: Till vs. Masvidal
